DESCRIPTION:2026-27 submissions are now open through April 10\, 2026. \nP
 lease CLICK HERE to submit your exhibition proposal.\nDittmar Memorial Gal
 lery at Norris University Center is an exhibition space and gathering plac
 e inviting the Northwestern University community to meaningfully interact 
 with art from varying perspectives. Through rotating exhibitions by emerg
 ing artists in the Evanston and Chicagoland area\, partnerships with organ
 izations and departments across the university\, and a permanent collectio
 n\, Dittmar prompts interdisciplinary dialogue through intentional engagem
 ent with the arts.Please note: we are not able to accommodate internationa
 l artists at this time.
LOCATION:Norris University Center\, 1999 Campus Drive\, Evanston\, IL
