SUMMARY:Storytelling Workshop with our own Rose Chord
DESCRIPTION:Evanston Writers Workshop\nJoin veteran performer Rose Chord (Am I Man Enough\, Hands Up\, The Brisrol Renaissance Faire) and learn the skills for live performance. From throwing focus to engaging the senses\, this 90 minute workshop will pass you all the tools you need to stand out and enrapture an audience.\n\n[Click Here](https://pci.jotform.com/form/260324506883155) to register for the class\n$15 for non-member\, $10 for members\n\nDue to the nature of this class it will be in-person only with limited space.
