BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Northwestern University": "https://wirtz.northwestern.edu/imagine-u-theatre-for-the-very-young/", "CitySpark Evanston": "https://artscircle.northwestern.edu/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Northwestern": "https://wirtz.northwestern.edu/imagine-u-theatre-for-the-very-young/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:northwestern
SUMMARY:Imagine U: Theatre for the Very Young presents Imagine That! & Spl
 ish\, Splash: A Day on the Lake
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T160000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T164500Z
UID:dd5b07ab267b489aeb53af50bc327626@northwestern.edu
DESCRIPTION:Director Ellie Levine\nCo-Creator Splish\, Splash: A Day on th
 e Lake Jamal Howard\nArtistic Mentor Lynn Kelso\nCreated in collaboration 
 with Northwestern Undergraduates and 2-5-year-olds at Total Child Preschoo
 l\nJoin us for a vibrant and engaging introduction to the magic of theatre
 \, specially designed for children aged 2-5 and their grown-ups. Two diffe
 rent remounted shows will take place: Imagine That! (3/7 and 3/15) and Spl
 ish\, Splash: A Day on the Lake (3/8 and 3/14).\nOur multi-sensory perform
 ances offer a delightful first taste of live theatre\, crafted by a dedica
 ted team of educational artists who specialize in early childhood developm
 ent alongside undergraduate students focused on theatre for young audience
 s. Come and experience the joy of interactive storytelling and creative ex
 ploration with your little ones!\nImagine That!\nAutumn\, Winter\, and Spr
 ing are on a mission to make a rainbow\, but they need the help of Summer
 —that’s you! In this interactive\, multi-sensory adventure\, preschool
  audiences will use the power of their imagination to bring the colors of 
 the seasons to life.\nApproximate run time: 45 minutes\nSuggested ages: 2-
 5\nSplish\, Splash: A Day on the Lake\nSet sail on a magical journey aroun
 d Lake Michigan! Through music\, puppetry\, and interactive experiences\, 
 our crew of young sailors will explore the wildlife and whimsy of the lake
 .\nApproximate run time: 45 minutes\nSuggested ages: 2-5
LOCATION:Wirtz Center: Hal & Martha Hyer Wallis Theater\, 1949 Campus Driv
 e\, Evanston\, IL
URL:https://wirtz.northwestern.edu/imagine-u-theatre-for-the-very-young/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston, Northwestern University
END:VEVENT
