 r Your Business. Stay Informed. The Lincoln Square Ravenswood Chamber of C
 ommerce \\(LSRCC\\) Legislative Series is your opportunity to connect dire
 ctly with elected officials and stay ahead of policies shaping the busines
 s community. Through a series of four annual events\, local entrepreneurs 
 and business leaders engage in meaningful discussions with City\, County\,
  State\, and Federal representatives. Why Attend? Gain first-hand insights
  into legislation impacting your business. Network with fellow entrepreneu
 rs and policymakers. Advocate for issues that matter to your industry. Sta
 y informed on key economic and policy trends. STATE OF THE NEIGHBORHOOD Ma
 rk your calendars! Join us on March 19\, 2026\, at 8:30 AM at Luna Cafe \\
 (5433 N Lincoln Ave\\) for our State of the Neighborhood Breakfast. Hear d
 irectly from Alderman Matt Martin and Alderperson Andre Vasquez as they pr
 ovide updates on the latest developments in City Hall and what's ahead for
  our business community. Learn more about the Legislative Series at  www.l
 incolnsquare.org/legislative-series .
