X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Shore Center": "https://northshorecenter.org/event/solstice/", "CitySpark Evanston": "https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=5#/details/solstice-a-winter-circus-experience/17366253/2026-03-22T19"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Shore Center": "https://northshorecenter.org/event/solstice/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:north_shore_center
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston, North Shore Center
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260322T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260322T190000
DTSTAMP:20260314T215433
CREATED:20251106T050114Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251106T185730Z
UID:10001182-1774206000-1774206000@northshorecenter.org
SUMMARY:Solstice: A Winter Circus Experience
DESCRIPTION:Step into a dreamscape with “Solstice: a Winter Circus Experience” by Circus EVO. At the heart of the story is a girl who loses her light and stumbles into a world where time bends\, memories breathe\, and the familiar becomes impossibly strange. Shadows dance\, snow drifts fall\, and acrobats blur the line between the everyday and the extraordinary. More than a circus\, “Solstice” is a living poem — a place where nostalgia meets surreal wonder\, and where audiences are invited to rediscover the childlike awe of seeing snow for the first time! \nIn 2026\, Solstice returns with all-new elements and an original score composed by NC artist Bella Nona\, weaving music\, movement\, and imagination into a one-of-a-kind celebration of the human spirit. Don’t Miss it! \n \nAbout Circus EVO:\nCircus EVO is an International Circus Company based in North Carolina. Since 2020 we’ve transformed urban spaces into vibrant stages\, bridging the gap between art and community through Contemporary Circus\, Dance\, Music\, Theater\, and more! Our Mission to EVOke Emotions and EVOlve Circus Art empowers Artists of all backgrounds\, while bringing a new way to entertain and provide cultural value to our community. \nOver the past 5 years\, we have emerged as a dynamic force\, dedicated to delivering high-quality\, multi-disciplinary performances. Since our inception\, Circus EVO has performed over 70 times in 11 cities for thousands of people\, supporting more than 70 artists and creatives along the way.
URL:https://northshorecenter.org/event/solstice/
LOCATION:George Van Dusen Theatre
CATEGORIES:Theatre
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://www.facebook.com/events/1375317127544086/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Mindy Smith at Space
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T190000
UID:251222wGbBtmS9AkOYiY1peDCNEw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/NwDmEYTo3UyUbxnnXaMlpg.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Good things\, its often said\, come to those who wait. And yet
 \, as one of the great poets of our time also famously observed\, the wait
 ing is the hardest part.Both truths have been proven once again on the jou
 rney to singer-songwriter Mindy Smiths sixth studio album Quiet Town\, whi
 ch brings a treasured musical voice back into the spotlight.Fans can look 
 forward to hearing new songs from Quiet Town as well as beloved tracks fro
 m her previous albums during her live performances.A good rule of thumb wh
 en going to a Mindy Smith concert\, bring a hanky\, a tissue or an extra s
 leeve. Your tear ducts dont know the difference between laughing tears and
  crying tears and youll likely be doing both. Humor is how I compensate fo
 r singing so many sad tunes back-to-back\, says Smith.Mindy Smith is a Lon
 g Island-born\, Americana award winning\, Dove nominated\, Nashville based
  singer-songwriter with a clear and honest passion for Americana\, jazz\, 
 pop\, rock\, blues\, and folk. As a recording artist\, she has sold over 7
 50k albums and singles and amassed over 175 million streams to date. She h
 as played some of the most prestigious festivals in the world including Ca
 mbridge Folk Festival\, Maverick Festival\, Newport Folk Festival\, Tellur
 ide Bluegrass Festival\, MerleFest\, Austin City Limits\, South by Southwe
 st\, Bonnaroo and more. Smith has also appeared on The Grand Ole Opry over
  20 times.Her original songs have been recorded and released by the likes 
 of Alison Krauss\, Lee Ann Womack\, Faith Hill and most recently Danny Bur
 ns ft Sam Bush. Mindy has performed with and toured alongside the likes of
  Dolly Parton\, Emmylou Harris\, Alison Krauss\, John Prine \\(US AND UK T
 our\\)\, Nickel Creek \\(US Tour\\)\, and Mary Chapin Carpenter \\(US Tour
 . Most recently\, Smith was the featured vocalist on Kenny Chesneys charti
 ng single\, Better Boat. Says Chesney\, if you just close your eyes and li
 sten to her voice -- Im speaking for me --she brings calm\, she brings a s
 ense that its all going to be all right. \\[T\\]o me\, when I hear her voi
 ce\, its like an angel\, her voice is so--whats the word?genreless. Its bi
 gger than all of us.
LOCATION:Evanston SPACE
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1375317127544086/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
