DESCRIPTION:This month we'll be discussing The Jasad Heir by Sara Hashem. 
 Silvia\, the Heir of Jasad\, should not have survived the destruction of h
 er family\, but she fled her kingdom and spent the next decade in hiding. 
 Forbidden magic flows through her veins\, and those in power raze cities i
 n order to extinguish it. When the enemy Nizhali prince discovers her magi
 c\, he strikes her a bargain: be his champion in the deadly Alcalah tourna
 ment. Win for his kingdom\, and she can earn her freedom. This is the fir
 st book in Sara Hashem's completed romantasy duology\, which is set in an 
 Egyptian-inspired fantasy world.Find The Jasad Heir in the library catalog
 .
