DESCRIPTION:Have you applied to Oakton College for Summer 2026 or Fall 2026
 ? Learn about (and even complete) your next steps before you can enroll in 
 your classes! Applicants are welcome to bring one guest.\n \n\nDuring this 
 session\, students can:\n\nComplete the Online Orientation on-siteComplete 
 placement testing or schedule a testing appointmentSubmit Proof of Residenc
 y Verify your program of study and explore Areas of InterestParticipate in 
 a brief financial aid check-inTake part in a campus tourStudents may stay f
 or the full session or as long as needed to complete these steps.\n\n \n\nI
 mportant Reminder: this is an optional event and does not fulfill ARW requi
 rements. If you plan to complete placement testing that day\, you must sche
 dule a testing appointment in advance through the website.\n\n\nPlease regi
 ster to confirm your attendance.\n\n\nFor questions\, please contact the Of
 fice of Admission at admission@oakton.edu or 847.635.1700.
