SUMMARY: Joan Ruppert | Making the Cut
DESCRIPTION:The Evanston Art Center (EAC) is excited to welcome the publi
 c to our upcoming exhibition\, Joan Ruppert | Making the Cut. The exhibit
 ion will be on display from March 28 - April 26\, 2026\, with an opening 
 reception on Sunday\, March 29\, from 1–4pm that will be free and open to
  the public.\n\nJoan Tortorici Ruppert is a television producer and media
  content creator based in Glenview\, IL. Her exhibition Making the Cut ht
 tps://www.evanstonartcenter.org/exhibitions/joan-ruppert-making-cut showc
 ases live-action collages that combine characters from her late father’s 
 vintage negatives together with contemporary environments. Each new colla
 ge is organic\, unpredictable\, and unrepeatable\, disrupting time and sp
 ace to write new chapters in her family’s story.
