DESCRIPTION:Join Native American & Indigenous Affairs and the Chicago Amer
 ican Indian Community Collaborative for our 10th annual Urban Native Educa
 tion Conference where we will facilitate the exchange of strategies\, tool
 s\, and research for Native American education in urban communities. Inter
 active workshops will be offered on various educational issues\, broadly c
 onstrued\, tackling the annual theme of Beyond Borders and Binaries.\nTo l
 earn more about this year’s conference and to register\, visit our websi
 te: https://chicagoaicc.com/10th-annual-urban-native-education-conference/
LOCATION:Parkes Hall\, 1870 Sheridan Road\, Evanston\, IL
