DESCRIPTION:Have you applied to Oakton College for Summer 2026 or Fall 2026
 ? Learn about (and even complete) your next steps before you can enroll in 
 your classes! Applicants are welcome to bring one guest.\n \n\nDuring this 
 session\, students can:\n\nComplete the Online Orientation on-siteComplete 
