X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://evanstonmade.org/event/jackalope-theatre-companys-the-dress-up-play-march-7-22-at-broadway-armory-park/2026-04-03/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Jackalope Theatre Company's "The Dress-Up Play\," March 7-22 at Br
 oadway Armory Park
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260403T080000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260403T090000
UID:2603018AWCXoXpuUmdY0pFT90IZg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/e3cbIN5pAEGwhrdO1dWDww.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Jackalope Theatre Company is proud to present its first produc
 tion for young audiences and the launch of its 18th season with the world 
 premiere of The Dress-Up Play by Juliet Kang Huneke\, March 7 – 22\, dir
 ected by Karina Patel\, at the Broadway Armory Park\, 5917 N Broadway St. 
 The running time is 60 minutes with no intermission.  \n\n  \n\nThe Dres
 s-Up Play is a new family-friendly production from Jackalope. New friends 
 gather in a bedroom to play dress up. But who gets to wear what? Do our cl
 othes have to match what we look like outside? And what if our outside doe
 sn’t match our inside? Filled with tutus\, fake mustaches\, scarves and 
 fierce runway walks. The Dress-Up Play is an immersive fashion party for a
 ll ages that celebrates self-expression\, open-mindedness and the wholenes
 s of everyone. \n\n  \n\nThe performance schedule is Fridays at 7 p.m. an
 d Saturdays and Sundays at 2 p.m. Tickets are $15 – $35 with student and
  Edgewater resident discounts available. Subscription and single tickets a
 re now available at JackalopeTheatre.org or call/text the box office at 77
 3.340.2543. \n\n 
LOCATION:Broadway Armory Park
URL:https://evanstonmade.org/event/jackalope-theatre-companys-the-dress-up
 -play-march-7-22-at-broadway-armory-park/2026-04-03/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
