BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=5#/details/unveiling-evanston-women-artists/17988797/2026-04-04T13"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Unveiling Evanston Women Artists
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T130000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T160000
UID:260212oUolXnkxQk2jqLNTzfszQw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/CT7F4yijQ0aXrT9eldBcGg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Women artists have historically remained in relative obscurity
  due to several factors including societal pressures prioritizing domestic
 ity and systemic exclusion. This exhibit showcases women artists from our 
 collection of 20th century art and seeks to open the door to many more und
 errepresented Evanston women artists. Exhibit opens February 14 and runs t
 hrough April 12\, 2026.
LOCATION:Evanston History Center
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/unveiling-evanston-women-artists/17988797/2026-04-04T13
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://evanstonmade.org/event/sketching-at-sketchbook/2026-04-04/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Sketching at Sketchbook Brewing Co
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T130000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T143000
UID:260215c4F8gVa6YUGChcsP0yob_Q
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/6PKYOrkW_k2FPZG3IHPpKQ.large.png
DESCRIPTION:This monthly sketching meetup is a fantastic way for sketchers
  of all stages to learn sketching techniques\, share what they make and me
 et new art friends! \n\nHosted at Sketchbook Brewing Co. in Evanston\, Gue
 st Artists are on hand with sketching tips and a variety of materials are 
 provided. \n\nFREE to attend and sketch\, click here to RSVP \n\nHosted on
  the First Saturday of the Month! \n\n821 Chicago Ave.\, 1-2:30p \n\nFIRST
  SATURDAYS \n\nThis even is part of Evanston Made’s First Saturday Evans
 ton Art Events\, a self-guided exploration of Evanston’s Creative Commun
 ity\, featuring art on display at venues across Evanston. Shop for handmad
 e goods\, meet small business owners\, enjoy a delicious meal\, learn to s
 ketch and make ART Friends! \n\nSee citywide event listings here. Google M
 ap at evanstonmade.org. \n\nEvanston Made \n\nEvanston Made started as a c
 ommunity arts initiative supported by a volunteer corps advocating for vis
 ibility and awareness of Evanston artists. INFO \n\nSketchbook Brewing \n\
 nSketchbook Brewing Co. is a locally owned and operated microbrewery. INFO
LOCATION:Sketchbook Brewing Co
URL:https://evanstonmade.org/event/sketching-at-sketchbook/2026-04-04/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
