DESCRIPTION:Join Downtown Evanston and&nbsp\;<a rel="noopener noreferrer" 
 href="https://www.wcofe.org/" target="_blank">The Woman's Club of Evanston
 </a> on Sunday\, April 26\, from noon to 2 p.m. for Downtown Evanston's an
 nual Earth Day Clean-Up<strong>&nbsp\;</strong>event aimed at fostering co
 mmunity engagement and environmental stewardship. Individuals\, families\,
  office groups\, students are all encouraged to lend a hand in making our 
 downtown business district a cleaner\, greener place to live\, work and vi
 sit!&nbsp\;<br /><br />Participants will gather at Fountain Square to get 
 outfitted with gloves\, bags and maps before heading out to pick-up litter
  and debris. When finished\, participants will bring the trash bags back t
 o Fountain Square for disposal.&nbsp\;
