UID:81e3e9d18df0258f39e225593545c004@northwestern.edu
DESCRIPTION:Each month\, we invite water experts to share their innovative
  work in a concise 15-minute presentation\, followed by refreshing network
 ing opportunities with snacks and drinks. These gatherings are designed to
  create meaningful connections within our water community while providing 
 insights into cutting-edge research and initiatives. Open to all students\
 , faculty\, and interested community members\, our Watering Holes offer a 
 perfect blend of education and social interaction in a welcoming environme
 nt.
LOCATION:O. T. Hogan Biological Sciences Building\, 2205 Tech Drive\, Evan
 ston\, IL
