 ng Tinkercad\, free and user-friendly software for creating 3D prints. In 
 this one-hour session\, you will learn the basics of 3D modeling\, navigat
 ing the platform\, and building simple models. You will pick up helpful ti
 ps and tricks to design your own project. Beginners welcome--no experienc
 e required. After the class\, you are welcome to finish your designs to su
 bmit them for 3D printing. Keyword: Consumer Information
CATEGORIES:DIY,Technology
