 ics:\n\nMarch 11: Evanston Women and the Fragile Nature of Legal Victories
  with Lori Osborne\, former director of the Evanston Women’s History Pr
 oject\n\nApril 8: Draining Evanston Part II: 21st Century with Dick Lanyo
 n\, former Executive Director of the Metropolitan Water Reclamation Distri
