SUMMARY:Teacher Focus Group
DESCRIPTION:We are developing new field trip programming for elementary school groups in preparation for the 2026-2027 school year. As part of that process\, we would love to get input from elementary school teachers. We have scheduled a focus group at the museum (3001 Central Street\, Evanston\, IL 60201) at 4:30 PM on Wednesday\, April 8th. If you teach students anywhere from pre-K to sixth grade and would like to be involved\, please RSVP. We will be closing the form for RSVPs on Monday\, April 6th. \nLight snacks and refreshments will be available.  \n\n			\n				RSVP\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				For more info about this program\, please contact Michael at mlamble@gichigamiin.org | (847) 475-0911
