SUMMARY:Ciné Club
DESCRIPTION:Alliance Française du North Shore\nJoin a group of *cinéphiles* online for a discussion in French of a French film with English subtitles.\n\nThe choice for this month is *Jules et Jim*. You'll watch the film on your own: view it for free on [Kanopy](https://www.kanopy.com/en/). For more details\, write to cine-club@AFnorthshore.org.\n\n**Membership in the AFduNS**\nWhile no membership is required for newcomers\, we welcome new members whose membership will support the activities of the AFduNS\, a nonprofit 501(c)(3) organization. For further info\, visit our [website](https://afnorthshore.org/) or [contact us](https://afnorthshore.org/contact-us). If you wish to join the AFduNS\, you may sign up [online](https://afnorthshore.org/join). Annual dues are $50.00.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/afnorthshore/events/308627471/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250624T132346Z
