BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Northwestern University": "https://www.northwestern.edu/norris/arts/dittmar-gallery/community-art-show.html", "CitySpark Evanston": "https://artscircle.northwestern.edu/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Northwestern": "https://www.northwestern.edu/norris/arts/dittmar-gallery/community-art-show.html"}
X-SOURCE-ID:northwestern
SUMMARY:Opening Reception: Community Art Show
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260409T230000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260410T010000Z
UID:0fa7aaf525578c81b128a7f825688123@northwestern.edu
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the opening reception of our annual community show
  which brings together artists from Northwestern\, Evanston and greater Ch
 icagoland communities to display their works in a group show. \nArt has b
 een used throughout human existence as a unifying force and a wordless lan
 guage to represent our curiosities\, communities\, and aspirations. Howeve
 r\, artistic spaces and practices have not always been inclusive or access
 ible to everyone. For this community show\, we invited artists to consider
  how their perspectives could be integrated to manipulate and redefine art
  in spaces in order to reclaim personal identities\, art practices\, and c
 ultures that have complex histories. Pieces were selected by how well they
  explored how creativity could be exercised to navigate the world and take
  ownership of reality. Artists were encouraged to consider stepping outsid
 e of the traditions of academic art to notice what they encounter in day-t
 o-day life that could be considered art.
LOCATION:Norris University Center\, 1999 Campus Drive\, Evanston\, IL
URL:https://www.northwestern.edu/norris/arts/dittmar-gallery/community-art
 -show.html
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston, Northwestern University
END:VEVENT
