SUMMARY:Sorting It Out: Understanding Winnetka's New Waste and Recycling To
 ols
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/sorting-it-out-38200
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251230T204521Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260207T220243Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a waste-related presentation highlighting programmi
 ng changes in Winnetka\, including the introduction of the Recycle Coach a
 pp\, the Hefty ReNew curbside collection for hard-to-recycle soft plastics
 \, and the sunsetting of the polystyrene drop-off collection at Winnetka P
 ublic Works. Christina Seibert\, Executive Director of the Solid Waste Age
 ncy of Northern Cook County\, and Elyse Steiner\, Sustainability Coordinat
 or for the Village of Winnetka\, will co-present with Liz Kunkle of Go Gre
 en Winnetka and Recycle Coach. This event is sponsored by Go Green Winnet
 ka.
CATEGORIES:Other
