 tos/jimmie-allen_MI0005520749-MN0003672595.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Jimmie Allen is one of the most dynamic and boundary-pushing a
 rtists in music today. His journey from Milton Delaware to the pinnacle of
  the music industry is powered by equal parts grit-genre-bending ambition 
 and an unmatched ability to to connect with audiences worldwide. After rel
 ocating to Nashville in 2007\, Allen spent years sharpening a sound that h
 onors storytelling tradition while leaning into pop-forward energy that re
 sonates across genres.
