 ortalimages/portalimages/647e2c9a-0c30-437e-b42e-10c07b3d22ba.large.PNG
DESCRIPTION:Run for the Dogs 5K features a fast\, flat\, and scenic course
  and proceeds from this event support Chicagoland Lab Rescue! \n\nJoin us 
 on Saturday\, April 18\, 2026 at either 8:30 am or 10:00 am for an excitin
 g event that features the scenic views of Blue Star Memorial Woods\, Glenv
 iew\, IL and supports Chicagoland Lab Rescue. With awesome swag for all do
