 r Medal\\_\n\n\\* Dog Charm\n\n\\* 5k Run/Walk Entry\n\n\\* Chip Timed Rac
 e Bib\n\n\\* Live Race Results\n\n\\* Finish Line Treats For Humans and Do
 gs! \n\nFor more info visit: https://runsignup.com/Race/IL/Glenview/Runfor
 theDogsGlenview?raceRefCode=X3W5wbMV
