BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://www.eths.k12.il.us/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Campus Tour
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T100000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T120000
UID:250708cu-vgeX9iEWKAj02vtnnlg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/7db019ee-e0af-4900-ab07-63bbda315a89.large.png
DESCRIPTION:The ETHS Campus Tour days are designed to provide a guided tou
 r  of the school's facilities. Each tour is approximately 60 minutes in du
 ra tion and includes visits to the athletics facilities\, career and techn
 ical  education wing\, libraries\, and fine arts/performing arts areas.\n\
 n \n\nProsp ective or new ETHS families\, District 202 community members\,
  business owne rs\, and people who work in Evanston/Skokie organizations o
 r businesses are  invited to attend. Please allow a total of 1.5 hours for
  this event. The  tour will last approximately 60 minutes followed by an o
 ptional 20-minute  Q&A session. Tours are hosted by ETHS staff with suppor
 t from ETHS Ambassa dors.\n\n \n\nWhile childcare is not provided\, childr
 en may attend ETHS Campus  Tour days with a registered adult\; please note
  that tours are not recomme nded for children under the age of 5 or people
  with limited mobility due t o extensive walking.\n\n \n\nRegistration for
  Campus Tours opens approximately  one month before each tour date. If you
 r preferred tour date is not avail able at this time\, please visit the re
 gistration page again soon. \n\n \n\nFor  more information\, contact the E
 THS Welcome Center at 847-424-7008.
LOCATION:ETHS Beardsley Gym
URL:https://www.eths.k12.il.us/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
