SUMMARY:Works of the Romantic Era
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T200000
UID:260309Py757KGqMUCfMMZpl8WoUA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/DTpngpn0tUG-iKJqNRBIAg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Wilmette Quartet sings works of the Romantic era including Dur
 ufle's Tantum Ergo\, Schuman's Abendfeier in Venedig\, and Brahms Liebesli
 eder. Vocalists are Maya Behiri \\(soprano\\)\, Zoë Kales \\(mezzo-sopr
 ano\\)\, Jordan Haas \\(tenor\\)\, and Aiden Kocian \\(baritone\\).
