X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=5#/details/michael-feinstein-and-linda-eder/17524212/2026-04-22T19"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Michael Feinstein and Linda Eder
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260422T193000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260422T193000
UID:260211y6_npY5o7EKnF5UC4tAN_Q
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/2FWiqSS50EKFLCaMTS-jDA.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Michael Feinstein and Linda Eder come together for a rare and 
 elegant evening celebrating the Great American Songbook and the power of t
 imeless American music. Feinstein\, the preeminent interpreter of classic 
 standards\, brings his signature piano artistry\, storytelling\, and deep 
 musical insight\, while Broadway favorite Linda Eder showcases her renowne
 d vocal power\, clarity\, and emotional depth. Together\, these two iconic
  performers blend classic American song\, soaring vocals\, and lush arrang
 ements in a warm and unforgettable concert experience\, launching North Sh
 ore Center?s 30th Anniversary season at the intimate George Van Dusen Thea
 tre.
LOCATION:Northlight Theatre
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/michael-feinstein-and-linda-eder/17524212/2026-04-22T19
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
