 -greatest-movie-action-scenes-and-stunts-filmed-35956
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251113T163821Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T222106Z
DESCRIPTION:With Chicago being so rich in varying and unique buildings and 
 landscapes\, it has set the stage for some of the largest action and movie
  stunts ever filmed.  We’ll take a look at some of those amazing movie 
 stunts as well as some of the most incredible action movie scenes. We’ll
  cover “The Hunter”\, “Dark Knight”\, Blues Brothers”\, “Trans
 formers”\, “Divergent”\, “Backdraft”\, and others.
