 rctic-35718
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251110T212646Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T161555Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Smithsonian magazine editor Meilan Solly for a deep dive i
 nto the Franklin expedition\, a failed search for the Northwest Passage th
 at resulted in the deaths of all 129 officers and crew members. Solly will
  discuss how long-overlooked Inuit testimony holds the key to understandin
 g what happened to the men after they vanished from the written record.
