DESCRIPTION:Join Downtown Evanston and The Woman&'s Club of Evanston on Su
 nday\, April 26\, 12-2pm for our annual Earth Day Clean-Up event aimed at 
 fostering community engagement and environmental stewardship. Individuals\
 , families\, office groups\, students are all encouraged to lend a hand in
  making our downtown business district a cleaner\, greener place to live\,
  work and visit! Participants will gather at Fountain Square to get outfit
 ted with gloves\, bags and maps before heading out to pick-up litter and d
 ebris. When finished\, participants will bring the trash bags back to Foun
 tain Square for disposal. Thanks to Brightview Landscaping for providing t
 he supplies and removing all trash collected during the event.
LOCATION:Evanston's Fountain Square
