X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=5#/details/the-little-dancer-a-reimagining-of-le-petit-prince/18287332/2026-04-26T14"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:The Little Dancer: A Reimagining Of Le Petit Prince
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260426T140000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260426T150000
UID:2603093z_9x8dLu0qIZR_U15GnLw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/snMzWdGD_EK_5mGlNRKjLA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Ede2 celebrates its 15th Anniversary with an original dance pr
 oduction “The Little Dancer: A Reimagining of Le Petit Prince” writt
 en by Antoine de Saint-Exupéry. The out-of-this-world production will fol
 low the story of a pilot marooned in the desert where they meet the myster
 ious stranger who traveled to Earth from a far away asteroid in search of 
 the meaning of connection and friendship. This family-friendly show featur
 es an eccentric cast of characters who populate various planets\, such as 
 space royalty\, a talking rose and a friendly fox\, who all teach The Litt
 le Dancer unique lessons on becoming a good person and how to care for oth
 ers. For ede2’s celebratory anniversary season\, the production will fea
 ture original music composed by Chicago Recording Academy Governor Tim Cor
 pus\, costume design by Josephine Everett\, Scenic Design by Daphne Agosin
  and Charlie Malave\, narration by Kelsey Cally and a lineup of profession
 al choreographers such as GREYSCALE Artistic Director Jessica Kondrath and
  Jus.Be House Collective’s co-founder Jordan Ordonez.
LOCATION:Studio5
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/the-little-dancer-a-reimagining-of-le-petit-prince/18287332/202
 6-04-26T14
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
