X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=5#/details/meals-on-wheels-northeastern-illinois-annual-gala/18135410/2026-04-30T17"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Meals on Wheels Northeastern Illinois Annual Gala
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260430T173000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260430T173000
UID:260217RbGrEeaPqEid9EURceV6cQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/EOMZi8cPKU-IRkGWVJej5Q.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our Annual Gala in support of Meals on Wheels Nort
 heastern Illinois! This special evening brings together supporters\, volun
 teers\, and community partners who share a commitment to nourishing both b
 ody and spirit across our region.\n\nSet in one of Evanston’s most beaut
 iful venues\, the night will celebrate the impact of daily meal delivery\,
  meaningful connections\, and the neighbors we serve. Guests will enjoy di
 nner \\(menu\\) featuring some of the same meals we proudly serve to our
  clients\, a silent auction\, a program highlighting stories of individual
 s who receive meals and others who have been deeply touched by our mission
 \, and a paddle raise.\n\nWe look forward to celebrating with everyone and
  sharing more about our initiative to double our meal output. Thank you fo
 r joining us ensure that no neighbor goes hungry or feels alone.
LOCATION:Woman's Club of Evanston
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/meals-on-wheels-northeastern-illinois-annual-gala/18135410/2026
 -04-30T17
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
