X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://www.infullswingjazzorchestra.com/international-jazz-day-2026"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Evanston Celebrates International Jazz Day!
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260430T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260430T212000
UID:2602174_wTYzWSgkCDXpzHTA46Hw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/pi07mEKK7EeidkyU8KU6mA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Evanston celebrates International Jazz Day with multi-generati
 onal performances\, including music from Evanston teen sensations “7th P
 eriod”\, Evanston’s homegrown quintet “Jazz Dads\,” and wrapping u
 p with Evanston’s venerable “In Full Swing” Jazz Orchestra. Special 
 guest artists Donovan Mixon on guitar\, and Chris Greene on saxophone will
  perform throughout the evening. \n\nThe free event will celebrate Americ
 a’s original art form from its earliest days in New Orleans to some of t
 oday’s most iconic tunes. Visit the concert’s web site and social medi
 a event pages for full details of this special concert. \n\nThe concert w
 ill begin at 7pm in Evanston’s newest venue - Akar Auditorium\, located 
 at 2715 Hurd Ave. in Evanston\, IL 60201
LOCATION:Former Second Church of Christ\, Scientist
URL:https://www.infullswingjazzorchestra.com/international-jazz-day-2026
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
