BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"CitySpark Evanston": "https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=5#/details/dog-man-the-musical/17366342/2026-05-02T15"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cityspark Evanston": "https://www.visitchicagonorthshore.com/events/dog-man-the-musical"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cityspark_evanston
SUMMARY:Dog Man the Musical
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T000000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T000000
UID:251206SnXTiA1Xkk-PMayDJIz5pQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/QkceX2BHGEyU5rqSxQY2uQ.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Based on the worldwide bestselling hit series by Dav Pilkey\, 
 Dog Man: The Musical is a hilarious and heartwarming production following 
 the chronicles of Dog Man\, who with the head of a dog and the body of a p
 oliceman\, loves to fight crime and chew on the furniture. But while tryin
 g his best to be a good boy\, can he save the city from Flippy the cyborg 
 fish and his army of Beasty Buildings? Can he catch Petey\, the world's mo
 st evil cat\, who has cloned himself to exact revenge on the doggy do-good
 er? And will George and Harold finish their show before lunchtime?? Find o
 ut in this epic musical adventure featuring the hilarity and heart of belo
 ved characters from Dav Pilkey\, the creator of Captain Underpants and Cat
  Kid Comic Club. Featuring an exciting book and lyrics by Kevin Del Aguila
 \, music by Brad Alexander\, and original direction and choreography by Je
 n Wineman. Recommended for ages 6\\+.
LOCATION:North Shore Center for the Performing Arts
URL:https://www.visitchicagonorthshore.com/events/dog-man-the-musical
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
