DESCRIPTION:This class is for all ages and abilities. You can practice on 
 a mat or in a chair. We have them both in studio!\n\nJoin Destini Brown Yo
 ga and Meditation Instructor \\+ Artist @peacelovedestini @designer.destin
 i\n\nMy wellness philosophy : My personal philosophy revolves around culti
 vating a fulfilling life characterized by peace\, emotional resilience\, a
 nd intentional simplicity. I am committed to nurturing self-love through r
 adical self-acceptance and extending compassion to others through authenti
 c connections. By embracing the spirit of self\, I find joy in physical ac
 tivity\, appreciate the abundance in my life\, and allow moments of creati
 ve expression to contribute to a serene and vibrant existence.
