BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Skokie Library": "https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/movie-night-23924"}
X-SOURCE-ID:skokie_library
X-SOURCE:Skokie Library
UID:23924
DTSTAMP:20260315T025448Z
SUMMARY:Movie Night
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/movie-night-23924
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260204T012921Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T173037Z
DESCRIPTION:Agent of HappinessBhutan measures happiness via the Gross Natio
 nal Happiness (GNH) index. Amber\, a happiness agent working for the gover
 nment\, surveys people across the country\, asking questions to ascertain 
 their happiness levels. Documentarians Arun Bhattarai and Dorottya Zurbó 
 follow Amber not only through his work and the diverse people he interview
 s\, but also through his personal life. The result is a touching and thoug
 ht-provoking exploration of happiness and sadness\, dreams and reality\, p
 rosperity and hardship\, companionship and loneliness\, as well as a subtl
 e scrutiny of the concept of GNH. Directed by Arun Bhattarai and Dorottya
  Zurbó.After watching the film\, share your questions and comments in a d
 iscussion with Chris and Sharon.2024 : 94 minutes : Not rated: Documentary
 In Nepali and Dzongkha with English subtitles.Free tickets will be given t
 o those who attend.Watch the trailer for Agent of Happiness.Find Agent of 
 Happiness in the library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Discussion,Movie
DTSTART:20260512T233000Z
DTEND:20260513T020000Z
LOCATION:5215 Oakton Street\, Skokie\, IL\, 60077\, US
ROOM:Petty Auditorium
GEO:42.0258969;-87.7580355
END:VEVENT
