 content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1
  group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min
 -w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1">\n<div class="flex max-w-full flex
 -col grow">\n<div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-co
