 n<div class="streaming-animation markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full w
 rap-break-word light markdown-new-styling">\n<p data-start="0" data-end="5
 96" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">The Main-Dempster Mile will 
 host the Evanston Arts &amp\; Craft Beverage Crawl on Thursday\, May 14\, 
 from 5 p.m. to 8 p.m.\, offering a one-night experience that blends local 
 art\, craft beverages\, and neighborhood businesses. The event will featur
 e pop-up art exhibits inside shops along Main Street\, Dempster Street\, a
 nd Chicago Avenue\, with tastings from Evanston-based craft beverage maker
 s\, including Sketchbook Brewing\, FEW Spirits\, and Kombucha Brava. All p
 roceeds from the crawl will benefit Evanston Made. Online ticket pre-sales
  begin February 2 and are available through May 12.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<
 /div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>
