DESCRIPTION:Part of the Mental Health Series for Adults presented by NAMI. 
 This presentation offers a powerful\, personal look at what it’s like to
  live with a mental health condition. Led by a speaker with lived experien
 ce\, this session will help reshape attitudes\, change assumptions\, deepe
 n your understanding of mental health\, and ask questions.The National All
 iance on Mental Illness (NAMI) is the nation’s largest grassroots mental
  health organization dedicated to building better lives for the millions o
 f Americans affected by mental illness.
CATEGORIES:Health
