DESCRIPTION:ElementalIn Element City\, air\, earth\, and water coexist\, ye
 t they live by one simple rule—elements cannot mix. One day\, Ember (fir
 e) meets Wade (water)\, and their friendship makes Ember rethink everythin
 g she knew about the world. From Walt Disney Pictures and Pixar Animation
  Studios. Featuring the voice talents of Leah Lewis\, Mamoudou Athie\, Ron
 nie del Carmen\, Shila Ommi\, Wendi McLendon-Covey\, and Catherine O'Hara.
  Directed by Peter Sohn.Free tickets will be given to all who attend.2023 
