DESCRIPTION:We Bought a ZooBenjamin Mee\, recently widowed with two childre
 n—14-year-old Dylan and 7-year-old Rosie—thinks that starting over wil
 l do them all good\, especially after Dylan gets expelled from school. Whi
 le looking to relocate\, they find a dilapidated old house that happens to
  come with a zoo that needs saving. There\, they meet zookeeper Kelly Fost
 er and her small\, dedicated staff\, who want to see it reopened. Despite 
 the huge financial commitment and having no experience\, Benjamin takes on
  the task with the help of his family.Loosely inspired by a true story\, t
 his is a healing adventure about second chances. Starring Matt Damon\, Sca
 rlett Johansson\, Thomas Haden Church\, Patrick Fugit\, and Elle Fanning. 
 Directed by Cameron Crowe.2011 : 124 minutes : Rated PG for language and s
 ome thematic elements : Comedy-dramaFree tickets will be given to all who 
 attend.Watch the trailer for We Bought a Zoo.Find We Bought a Zoo in the l
 ibrary catalog.
CATEGORIES:Movie
