DESCRIPTION:Queen of GloryWriter-director-actor Nana Mensah does triple dut
 y in this film. The story centers on Sarah Obeng (Mensah)\, a Ghanaian Ame
 rican PhD student in molecular neuro-oncology at Columbia University. She 
 is about to relocate to Ohio with her married boyfriend when news comes th
 at her mother has died unexpectedly. Sarah returns to the Bronx to settle 
 her affairs\, which include inheriting a Christian bookstore called King 
 of Glory\, and she finds herself navigating the expectations of Ghanaian r
 elatives and the community while figuring out what she wants and needs. S
 tarring Nana Mensah\, Meeko Gattuso\, Oberon K.A. Adjepong\, Adam Leon\, R
 ussell G. Jones\, and Anya Migdal. Directed by Nana Mensah.After watching 
 the film\, share your questions and comments in a discussion with Chris an
 d Sharon.2021 : 78 minutes : not rated: Comedy-dramaFree tickets will be g
 iven to those who attend.Watch the trailer for Queen of Glory.Find Queen o
 f Glory in the library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Discussion,Movie
