DESCRIPTION:Drop in for one-on-one practice to help you prepare for your ci
 tizenship interview.During the citizenship interview\, an immigration offi
 cer will ask you about your application and background. You will also need
  to take an English and civics test.Please bring your completed N-400 appl
 ication if you have one. Stop by HIAS Immigration & Citizenship’s info
 rmation table\, where you can learn about resources and ask questions on a
  wide range of immigration topics.All information shared will be confident
 ial.
