DESCRIPTION:Celebrate USA's 250th birthday with a fun\, hands-on journey ac
 ross the country. We'll explore the 50 states through stories\, games\, an
 d movement activities. Travel from region to region and collect stamps al
 ong the way—no suitcase required! Free tickets will be given to all who
  attend. For grade K-2. Kids younger than eight must have an adult in the 
 library during the event.   Keyword: USA 250
