BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-ID:evanston_bike_club
X-SOURCE:Evanston Bike Club
UID:TU2051767182
DTSTAMP:20260315T011111Z
SUMMARY:Annual EBC Picnic (Mary Fry)
DESCRIPTION:Status: PENDING!\n\nLeader: Mary Fry\n\n## Our annual EBC picni
 c at Evanston's Lighthouse Park(Central/Sheridan):\n\nThe day begins with 
 a morning ride and culminates in a potluck lunch. Check the Rides Calendar
  to find the perfect ride for you. All rides begin and end at the Lighthou
 se Beach Park. Please bring a dish to share that does not spoil easily\, (
 no mayonnaise salads\, raw meat/there is no grill). Beginning @ 8:00 AM\, 
 coolers and a watchful eye will be available for food. The club will provi
 de soda\, plates/eating utensils\, and veggie and meat roll-ups.\n\nWhethe
 r or not you ride\, please come to the picnic. We always have a good time!
  (No alcoholic beverages. That would be a violation of park rules). Questi
 ons\, suggestions\, or volunteer to help\, tele/text Mary Fry @ 773-383-24
 66.\n\n
LOCATION:Evanston Lighthouse Park
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:TRUE
CATEGORIES:_Meetings/Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
