SUMMARY:Chandler to Belmont (Doug Hoffman)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Casual\n\nDistance: 24 miles\n\nLead
 er: Doug Hoffman\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/River%20Run%20Bridge.
 jpg This week's Thursday Casual ride will take off eastbound from Chandler
  to the lakefront\, then south into Chicago. From Rogers Ave. we'll go sou
 th on the bike route west of Sheridan Road\, mostly Greenview Ave. At Berw
 yn Ave. we'll head west and later south to pick up the trail along the Nor
 th Branch of the Chicago River\, including the Riverview Bridge. At Belmon
 t we'll turn around to head back north\, along the River and then the cana
 l along McCormick. Lunch will be in Ravenswood Manor or Ravenswood. We wil
 l discuss places to eat Thursday before departure.\n\n
LOCATION:Chandler Park\, Evanston
CATEGORIES:..Casual (10-12 mph),.Weekly > ...Casual Wkly
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
