SUMMARY:Thanksgiving & Day After Thanksgiving Show & Go Rides
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Casual\, Moderate\, Fast\, Fast Plus
 \, Very Fast\n\n# ***!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Thanksgiving.jpgThan
 ksgiving &amp\; Day After Thanksgiving Show &amp\; Go Rides:***\n\n**The d
 estination and distance will be decided by the group at the meeting time. 
 Riders must sign an up-to-date sign-in &amp\; waiver sheet (from EBC websi
 te) and theremust be at least two people on the ride\, with the leader bei
 ng a current club member. Club members are usually available to lead these
  rides\, but if no club member is available\, the ride will not be held.**
 \n\n- **Casual Show &amp\; Go Ride (10-12) -**Distance is typically 20 to 
 30 miles with a snack stop. Ride Info: JoG 773.271.5802 jigcsr@gmail.com\n
 - **Moderate Show &amp\; Go Ride (13-15 mph) -**Distance is typically 30 t
 o 45 miles with a snack stop.Ride Info: DanaT 847.363.6306 danataylor1@com
 cast.net\n- **Fast Show &amp\; Go Ride (15-17 mph) -**Distance is typicall
 y 35 to 45 miles with a lunch stop. Ride Info: JeffM 312.354.0080 jeff\\_m
 iller@aol.com: mailto:jeff_miller@aol.com\n- **Fast Plus Show &amp\; Go Ri
 de (17-19 mph) -**Distance is typically 40 to 80 miles with a snack stop. 
 Ride Info: TomW 630.240.9023 **wittto@comcast.net**\n- **Very Fast Show &a
 mp\; Go Ride (19-21 mph) -**Distance is typically 40 to 80 miles with a sn
 ack stop. Ride Info: JayT 312.925.3085jaytwery@gmail.com\n\n
LOCATION:Panera Wilmette
