UID:TU2028949009
DTSTAMP:20260315T011111Z
SUMMARY:Club Meeting: Annual Holiday Pot Luck (Evanston Bicycle Club)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Any\n\nLeader: Evanston Bicycle Club
 \n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Holiday%20Potluck.jpg The annual Holi
 day Potluck will be held on Tuesday\,  \nDecember 15th at 6:30 pm at the E
 vanston Ecology Center.  \nAll EBC members are invited to the dinner. Plea
 se bring a dish to share with a utensil for serving. Label your container 
 and utensil and include a brief description of your dish to assist those w
 ho may have any food sensitivity. Plates\, utensils\, napkins\, cups\, and
  beverages will be provided. If you would like to assist with setting up t
 he potluck or have any questions\, contact Joan Welch at jwelch4252@gmail.
 com or (843) 729-0705. See you at 6:30 pm\, Tuesday\, December 15th at Rob
 ert Crown!\n\n
LOCATION:Evanston Ecology Center
CATEGORIES:_Meetings/Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
