SUMMARY:Christmas Day Show & Go Rides
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Casual\, Moderate\, Fast\, Fast Plus
 \, Very Fast\n\n## ***!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Christmas%20Day.jpg
 ***\n\n# ***Christmas Day Show &amp\; Go Rides:***\n\n**The destination an
 d distance will be decided by the group at the meeting time. Riders must s
 ign an up-to-date sign-in &amp\; waiver sheet (from EBC website) and there
 must be at least two people on the ride\, with the leader being a current 
 club member. Club members are usually available to lead these rides\, but 
 if no club member is available\, the ride will not be held.**\n\n- **Casua
 l Show &amp\; Go Ride (10-12) -**Distance is typically 20 to 30 miles with
  a snack stop. Ride Info: JoG 773.271.5802 jigcsr@gmail.com\n- **Moderate 
 Show &amp\; Go Ride (13-15 mph) -**Distance is typically 30 to 45 miles wi
 th a snack stop.Ride Info: DanaT 847.363.6306 danataylor1@comcast.net\n- *
 *Fast Show &amp\; Go Ride (15-17 mph) -**Distance is typically 35 to 45 mi
 les with a lunch stop. Ride Info: JeffM 312.354.0080 jeff\\_miller@aol.com
 : mailto:jeff_miller@aol.com\n- **Fast Plus Show &amp\; Go Ride (17-19 mph
 ) -**Distance is typically 40 to 80 miles with a snack stop. Ride Info: To
 mW 630.240.9023 **wittto@comcast.net**\n- **Very Fast Show &amp\; Go Ride 
 (19-21 mph) -**Distance is typically 40 to 80 miles with a snack stop. Rid
 e Info: JayT 312.925.3085jaytwery@gmail.com\n\n
LOCATION:Panera Wilmette
CATEGORIES:..Casual (10-12 mph),..Moderate (13-15 mph),.Fast (15-17 mph),.F
 ast Plus (17-19 mph),.Very Fast (19-21 mph)
