X-TEAMUP-STATUS:PENDING!
X-TEAMUP-PACE:Moderate
X-TEAMUP-DISTANCE:32 miles
X-TEAMUP-START-LOCATION:Panera Wilmette
X-TEAMUP-LEADER:Sara Polonsky
END:VEVENT
