SUMMARY:Barrington Moretti's (Will Heelan)
DESCRIPTION:Status: CHANGES PENDING!\n\nPace: Fast\n\nDistance: 50 Miles\n\
 nLeader: Will Heelan\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png: 
 https://ridewithgps.com/routes/39695420\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/ca
 l/Barrington%20Hills.jpgStart: Village Green Park in Northbrook (corner of
  Walters &amp\; Meadow) at 9 am. If you drive to the start\, the streets m
 ay have parking restrictions if there is a festival in the park. There is 
 a parking lot on Walters just southeast of the park where you should be ab
 le to park.\n\nWe will ride through Long Grove and the rolling hills of Ba
 rrington Hills\, passing horse farms and mansions. Then our route drops do
 wn to our lunch stop at the Moretti's in Barrington. After lunch we return
  on beautiful Old Checker Road before stopping at Culver's for a quick res
 t/snack. The pace will be Fast (15-17 mph).\n\n
LOCATION:Northbrook Village Green
CATEGORIES:.Fast (15-17 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20270703T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20270703T090000
