SUMMARY:First Draft Grayslake (Will Heelan)
DESCRIPTION:Status: PENDING!\n\nPace: Fast\n\nDistance: 54 Miles\n\nLeader:
  Will Heelan\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png!https://e
 bcrides.org/images/cal/First%20Draft%20Grayslake.jpg: https://ridewithgps.
 com/routes/39835533The route starts at the Village green in Northbrook. It
  goes up through Libertyville to Gray's Lake where we have lunch at First 
 Draft Grayslake. It returns through scenic Independence Grove FP in Libert
 yville then back to Village Green.\n\nhttps://firstdraftgrayslake.net/gray
 slake-first-draft-food-menu\n\n
LOCATION:Northbrook Village Green
CATEGORIES:.Fast (15-17 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
